<item>
            <title>[LU-10679] Interop master/b2_10: ost-pools test 20 fails with &apos;&apos;Dir &apos;&apos;/mnt/lustre/d20.ost-pools/dir1/dir3&apos;&apos; is in pool: testpool&apos;&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10679</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ost-pools test_20 fails with &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;ost-pools test_20: @@@@@@ FAIL: Dir &apos;/mnt/lustre/d20.ost-pools/dir1/dir3&apos; is in pool: testpool
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test started failing with this error on 2018-01-26; &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/e9a745b3-182c-48c7-839f-26b07f3cb95c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/e9a745b3-182c-48c7-839f-26b07f3cb95c&lt;/a&gt;.  Since the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8264&quot; title=&quot;lfs setstripe without -p pool_name doesn&amp;#39;t inherit pool from parent/ROOT directory&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8264&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-8264&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20849/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20849/&lt;/a&gt;, landed to master on 2018-01-25, but has not landed to b2_10, I suspect this change is the reason for this failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#8217;ve only seen this test consistently fail in interop testing, 2.10.x clients with master servers. Logs for some failures are at:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/6ffc4f06-1288-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/6ffc4f06-1288-11e8-a7cd-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
